use-a-transition-period-in-starter-box:d: Vets recommend for dogs to undergo a transition period when changing to a new diet – especially if there has been little or no change over the years to the previous diet. In the early stages of a new diet, your dog may experience some watery poops if transitioned too quickly; this is perfectly normal and nothing to be concerned about. While transitioning isn’t an exact science, OCELLE suggests slowly transitioning your dog on to the new diet with smaller portions over a 7-day period, to enable time to adjust to the OCELLE goodness!

AboutUs.block-1-content-1: Term of endearment: “My little eye,” “my dearest,” “my precious one, or “apple of my eye.”
AboutUs.block-1-content-2: Used affectionately to address a loved one.
AboutUs.block-1-content-3: Treasured object or person: Something or someone held in high regard and considered valuable.
AboutUs.block-2-content-1: OCELLE starts not in a lab, but in a loving home. Our founder, Kevan, faced a challenge many pet parents know only too well – a beloved furry family member with unique needs. Kevan’s dog, Charlie, wasn’t just picky; he struggled with allergies, making mealtimes a constant battle.
AboutUs.block-2-content-2: Despite trying an array of regular brands and diets, nothing suited Charlie. The breakthrough came with a simple suggestion from his Vet: Why not try homemade meals? Sceptical but determined, Kevan swapped processed foods for real, home-cooked meals.
AboutUs.block-2-content-3: The transformation was nothing short of miraculous. Charlie, previously lethargic and uninterested, began to thrive. His allergies subsided, his energy returned, and his tail wouldn’t stop wagging.
AboutUs.block-3-content-1: This personal journey sparked an idea: What if I could extend this increase in health and happiness to all dogs? Why should real food be an exception rather than the norm for our beloved pets?
AboutUs.block-4-content-1: That’s how OCELLE was born. Our philosophy is straightforward: Real, nourishing food isn’t a pet’s privilege; it’s their right. We believe in the connection between diet and well-being, mirroring the importance of food in all our lives. No one should have to rely on the same processed foods, day in, day out, all year round.
AboutUs.block-4-content-2: OCELLE isn’t just about providing dog food; we’re redefining what pet nutrition actually means, and how we can all apply it in our homes, with ease.
AboutUs.block-4-content-3: After extensive research into pet nutrition, with insights from leading Vet Nutritionists, we’ve developed a range of fresh, convenient pet food solutions, that are both innovative and ground-breaking!
AboutUs.block-4-content-4: Our recipes aren’t just human-grade in quality; they’re meticulously crafted to promote your dog’s health and happiness, with the same love and care you’d put into creating a family meal.
AboutUs.block-4-content-5: Welcome to OCELLE, where your dog’s well-being isn’t just our business—it’sour heartfelt commitment.
AboutUs.block-5-title-1-2: We Turn Love Into Uncomplicated Care!
